well go to the advanced tab and were it says applications click there

then type in your server-ip ex.(blisterscape.no-ip.info) my server
then type in 43594 in all other boxes if its non-pk and 5555 if it is pk
and the dropdown boxes put in either both or tcp use both first then if u dont got that use tcp save it and it should work
run your server put in your port and your ip and there u go
